"title": "5165: listening",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5165",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>People are called upon to listen attentively to God's word, to his Son and also to words of wisdom. Christians must not only listen to God's word but also put it into practice. Those who refuse to listen to God's word or to correction are condemned.</p>\n<h2>The importance of listening</h2>\n<h3>To God's word and his spokesmen</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:10\">1SA 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:15\">2CH 20:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:8\">PSA 81:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:3-Jer26:6\">JER 26:3–26:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:2\">MIC 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:14\">ACT 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:16\">ACT 13:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:28\">ACT 28:28</a></p>\n<h3>To Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27\">JHN 10:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:10\">MAT 15:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:14\">MRK 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:16\">LUK 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:39\">LUK 10:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:8\">JHN 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:16\">JHN 10:16</a></p>\n<h3>To words of wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:20\">PRO 19:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:19\">JAS 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:11\">PSA 34:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:7\">PRO 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:24\">PRO 7:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:32-Prov8:34\">PRO 8:32–8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:15\">PRO 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:1\">PRO 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:31\">PRO 15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:46\">LUK 2:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should not listen to false prophets or ungodly suggestions</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:16\">JER 23:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:1-Deut13:3\">DEU 13:1–13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:6-Deut13:8\">DEU 13:6–13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:9\">JER 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:14-Jer27:17\">JER 27:14–27:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:8-Jer29:9\">JER 29:8–29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:19\">EZK 13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1\">1JN 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:5-1John4:6\">1JN 4:5–4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:10\">2JN 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>The wicked refuse to listen to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:7\">EZK 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:13\">EXO 7:13</a> <em>Pharaoh's refusal to listen</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:14\">2KI 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:40\">2KI 17:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:12\">2KI 18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:17\">NEH 9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:11\">PSA 81:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:12\">ISA 65:12</a>JER <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:13\">7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:26-Jer7:27\">JER 7:26–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:17\">JER 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:11\">JER 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:23\">JER 17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:21\">JER 22:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:3\">JER 25:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:7\">JER 25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:19\">JER 29:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:33\">JER 32:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:14\">JER 34:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:15\">JER 35:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:17\">JER 35:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:2\">JER 37:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:15\">JER 38:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:5\">JER 44:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:16\">JER 44:16</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:8\">EZK 20:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:11-Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:11–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:2\">MAL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:29-Luke16:31\">LUK 16:29–16:31</a></p>\n<h2>Those who refuse to listen to correction are condemned</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:15-Matt18:17\">MAT 18:15–18:17</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God's people must not only listen to God's word but also put it into practice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:28\">LUK 11:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22-Jas1:24\">JAS 1:22–1:24</a></strong> <em>In Hebrew and Greek the verb “listen” is related by the verb “to obey”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:32\">EZK 33:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:47-Luke6:49\">LUK 6:47–6:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:13\">ROM 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people listening</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:10\">GEN 18:10</a> <em>Sarah at the tent entrance</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:5\">GEN 27:5</a> <em>Rebekah to Isaac</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:9-1Sam3:10\">1SA 3:9–3:10</a> <em>Samuel to God</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:27\">PRO 19:27</a> <em>a son to instruction</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:46\">LUK 2:46</a> <em>Jesus Christ to the teachers of the law</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:1\">LUK 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:45\">LUK 20:45</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:39\">LUK 10:39</a> <em>Mary to Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:14\">ACT 16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25\">ACT 16:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:29\">ACT 26:29</a></p>",
